title: Amber Buxom Big & Healthy Lip Polish from Bare Escentuals
description: A Buxom babe is all about curves, tingles and attitude - and that includes the lips. Plump what you've got with our luscious polish, which naturally creates the look of fuller, more voluptuous lips. You'll know it's working when a tingly, cooling sensation rushes over you.

title: D & G Light Blue By Dolce & Gabbana For Women. Eau De Toilette Spray 1.6 Ounces
description: Introduced in 2001. Fragrance notes: rose, apple, musk and jasmine. Recommended use: casual.When applying any fragrance please consider that there are several factors which can affect the natural smell of your skin and, in turn, the way a scent smells on you.  For instance, your mood, stress level, age, body chemistry, diet, and current medications may all alter the scents you wear.  Similarly, factor such as dry or oily skin can even affect the amount of time a fragrance will last after being applied
